{"tid":1447910,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"親　有膽街頭勇武　無膽機場勇武？","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T23:33:07.000Z","uid":279326,"like":17,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"824b187c5085b2296a6433f96b57dacfceaace5f","tid":1447910,"uid":279326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:00.000Z","msg":"唔Ｌ妥就起我底<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1439595/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1439595/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n話Ｌ左３０萬人係街　都唔夠１０萬人係機場<br />\n<br />\n機場運作唔到　就有贏既機會　俾人爆頭嬲唔嬲<br />\n<br />\n俾黑警扮示威者捉自己人嬲唔嬲　太古俾人１米射布袋彈嬲唔嬲<br />\n<br />\n日Ｌ日係街頭又唔敢麻包袋　全部同我入機場玩大佢"},{"pid":"cfe6d5a94abc8380cb2e22a716229f2a9bceb311","tid":1447910,"uid":279326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:13.000Z","msg":"全部同我入機場"},{"pid":"bc1fe82a04d211d72d80a30c0a6eb0304ce5ad53","tid":1447910,"uid":279326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:23.000Z","msg":"全部同我入機場"},{"pid":"1dd097d3e8930c8cb646e1c836c890ff66e72b3e","tid":1447910,"uid":279326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:18:03.000Z","msg":"全部同我入機場"},{"pid":"466eefa1464bc92608616f0bc72ce0cee6d74a11","tid":1447910,"uid":279326,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:20:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>眼都俾人射爆埋阿<br />\nＢＥ　乜春野ＷＡＴＥＲ阿<br />\n我要香港機場運作唔到<br />\n即刻攬炒　唔去做既唔好話自己係勇武派</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"52dc7dcbe0b6572f16ee288e17d807a5ffdd9345","tid":1447910,"uid":279326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jaeRan6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjaeRan6.jpg&h=a134f2ce&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>你地對唔對得住無左隻眼既絲打<br />\n要打就係機場決一死戰<br />\n放ＴＧ唔走<br 